item.title: First Model Made!
item.dc:creator: @wayzey wayzey
item.description:
@wayzey wrote:

You should find a guide on youtube or something and learn how to model from scratch.

The end result is much better and you end up with a result that is actually half decent.

This is obviously a recolour though you have modified the object a bit and though it isn’t that great you’re 10x better than most people on this forum(sadly) and that shows that your second model could be half decent and original(made entirely by you).
Trust me unless you’re making an NPC specifically for a server make your entire object/weapon/etc from scratch or use a picture to aid you.
Oh and that doesn’t mean you post the NPC.

Read full topic
